                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "3b8903b9-8d46-4278-8437-914c3ccb7e67",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I am rather certain that all of you own some sort of magic item. They are rather ubiquitous, are they not? Today, we are going to discuss magic items and how they are created.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "9a8875d9-1eb4-4d27-a394-b5b252064063",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Magic items differ from runestones in that the items do not require Mojo to activate or work. The Mojo was bound into the item when it was created. Thus, magic items take a great deal of Mojo to create.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "be633947-287d-4db2-8755-6ecfa36e5f19",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Most Magic Users do not have this amount of Mojo. Therefore, they store up their Mojo in a magical staff or a Spongea runestone for several days before they set out to make a magic item.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "46d36582-3841-4458-8d45-00fa7e8e795b",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, you will each get a Spongea runestone to use in class. You will be storing around half of your available Mojo in the runestone in order to make a magic item tomorrow.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "aaf28434-3303-445d-88c8-772d2f158b2c",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Of course, it will take far more than a little Mojo to create an item that will continue to radiate a magical spell. We will need to use some alchemy and some inherently magical components.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "91c543c2-6a26-49c2-a909-94cb6d7ebe1f",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We will get started on making a magic item by working on your Spongea runestone to store your Mojo.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "a8dd724c-b57c-4afb-9f8b-b1693f5a4186",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Let us begin...",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "e899c3bb-4d41-4140-a162-adb553b2e742",
